      • buildAcronim

        public static String buildAcronim(String term0)
        Given a term return their possible Acronym. For example, for Informacion Systems it returns IS. If the term is made by a single word only, it returns an empty string.
        Parameters:
        term0 - the term to be evaluated.
        Returns:
        the guessed acronym or an empty string if the term is a single word.
